articles.description: The Jayhawks are able to control their fate in the Big 12 race once again, after rallying to defeat West Virginia at home on Saturday.

videos.description: J.P. Macura gets the Musketeers off to a hot start, scoring the team's first six points with a pair of 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Xavier's Macura hot from deep early

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Xavier's Macura hot from deep early) 2018/02/17 ESHEET

videos.description: Musketeers guard Quentin Goodin drives and dishes a highlight-reel pass to Sean O'Mara who rises up to slam home a contested slam.
videos.headline: Xavier's Goodin throws sweet behind-the-back pass

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Xavier's Goodin throws sweet behind-the-back pass) 2018/02/17 ESHEET

videos.description: Villanova guard Donte DiVincenzo comes up with a steal then bounces it to Omari Spellman in transition for a powerful slam.
videos.headline: Spellman flushes one-handed jam

videos.description: Villanova guard Jalen Brunson tosses a lob to Mikal Bridges who jumps above his defender to corral the pass and dunk it home.
videos.headline: Bridges skies for alley-oop slam

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bridges skies for alley-oop slam) 2018/02/17 ESHEET

videos.description: Xavier's Trevon Bluiett drives, absorbs contact and tosses up a layup that rolls all the way around the rim before dropping in for an and-1 score.
videos.headline: Bluiett gets bounce for bucket

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bluiett gets bounce for bucket) 2018/02/17 ESHEET

videos.description: Xavier guard Quentin Goodin passes to Trevon Bluiett who knocks down a contested 3-ball to get the hoop and the harm.
videos.headline: Bluiett converts 4-point play

videos.description: Villanova's Omari Spellman and Xavier's Paul Scruggs are each assessed technical fouls after the two get tangled up and get in each other's faces.
videos.headline: Tempers flare between Villanova, Xavier

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Tempers flare between Villanova, Xavier) 2018/02/17 ESHEET

videos.description: With the shot clock winding down, Villanova's Mikal Bridges bounces a pass between two defenders and Dhamir Cosby-Roundtree jams it home.
videos.headline: Bridges drops dime to set up Villanova dunk

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bridges drops dime to set up Villanova dunk) 2018/02/17 ESHEET

videos.description: Collin Gillespie misses a 3, but Omari Spellman hustles to poke the ball away from Xavier, and Gillespie knocks down his second attempt from deep.
videos.headline: Gillespie connects on second-chance triple

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Gillespie connects on second-chance triple) 2018/02/17 ESHEET
